arch elf
msg
@match gate
I keep it locked, so nobody can't steal
anything. If you promise not to steal
anything I can open the gate.
@match boots|box|chest|longbow
So you have been visited my private
chamber! Maybe I should keep that
door locked like gate!
@match adventurer|people
People like you.
@match buy|item|misc|sell|sold
I buy almost everything that people
are selling to me.
@match help|shop
This shop is specialized to missile
weapons such as bows and crossbows.
I have two rooms of them. The first
room contains miscellaneous items that
other adventurers have sold to me.
@match *
@addtopic gate
Welcome my little shop. How can I help
you ?
endmsg
